---
id: com.example.fixture.pkg-a
name: PkgA
version: 1.0.0
---

Fixture package: declares the `Task` ECHO type and a factory.
Used by `@dxos/introspect`'s test suite to verify symbol extraction
against realistic DXOS shapes (Schema.Struct + Type.object + annotations).

## Extensions

| Term       | URI                              |
| ---------- | -------------------------------- |
| `echo-type`| `org.dxos.mdl.echo-type@1.0`     |
| `op`       | `org.dxos.mdl.op@1.0`            |

## Types

```mdl
echo-type Task
  desc: A simple task item with title, optional description, and a done flag.
  echo-schema:
    typename: com.example.type.Task
    version:  0.1.0
  fields:
    title:        string             # description: Short summary of the task.
    description?: string             # description: Longer free-form notes about the task.
    done:         boolean             # description: Whether the task has been completed.
  label: title                        # LabelAnnotation — display label field
```

## Operations

```mdl
op make
  desc: Construct a new Task with `done` defaulted to false.
  input:
    title:        string
    description?: string
    done?:        boolean
  output: Task
  note: wraps Obj.make(Task, ...)
```

---

## Appendix: Extension Definitions

```mdl
ext echo-type
  uri: org.dxos.mdl.echo-type@1.0
  extends: type
  desc: An ECHO object type — a Schema.Struct with Type.object metadata and annotations.
  adds-fields:
    echo-schema: { typename: URI, version: SemVer }
    label?:      Identifier            # field used for display label
```

```mdl
ext op
  uri: org.dxos.mdl.op@1.0
  desc: A named operation with typed inputs, outputs, and declared errors.
  fields:
    desc?:   Prose
    input?:  FieldMap
    output?: TypeExpr
    errors?: ErrorMap
    note?:   Prose
```
